i-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-14-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576414\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576414\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining area with glass table, six chairs, decorative vases, and staircase beside large windows; artwork and sideboard are visible in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-15-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDescending into the basement reveals one of the home’s most surprising elements – a column-free space filled with natural light from a sunken courtyard. This level houses a vibrant lounge, a bar, and a play zone, shifting the conventional notion of what a basement can be.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576415\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576415\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern dining room with a glass table, eight upholstered chairs, striped wood wall panels, and marble accent wall; a potted plant and decorative items complete the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-16-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576416\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576416\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern room with a tufted chair, a dark coffee table with books and a candle, a small side table with a Buddha head, and a large window overlooking green plants and a textured wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-17-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576417\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576417\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room with neutral tones, cane armchairs, a white sofa, a patterned rug, and a tropical-themed wall mural with palm trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-18-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576418\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576418\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A man walks through a modern interior with marble floors, a glass elevator, wooden accents, and contemporary furniture.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-19-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576419\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576419\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a curved sofa, armchairs, wooden coffee table, built-in TV, large windows, and minimalist decor in neutral tones.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-20-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe upper level rooms were designed for each inhabitant. The primary suite is a tranquil hideaway; the daughter’s room expresses soft curves and pastel hues; while the son’s space merges function and solitude with a study nook that opens to the terrace. “This is where the family finds their quietest, most personal moments,” says Arora. “Each space is a true reflection of who they are.” A meditation room offers a quiet escape, while the terrace becomes a gathering point under the open sky – a platform for reflection and shared moments.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576420\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576420\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-810x810.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a large bed, neutral-toned bedding, wooden partition, abstract rug, ceiling fan, and floor-to-ceiling curtains allowing natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-810x810.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-800x800.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-100x100.jpg 100w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-768x768.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-300x300.jpg 300w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-21-810x810.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576421\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576421\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a large bed, neutral bedding, decorative pillows, a nightstand with vases, and floor-to-ceiling sheer curtains letting in natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-22-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576422\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576422\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with wood panel walls, a bed with neutral bedding and pillows, a nightstand with two white vases and a small flower arrangement, and an open door leading to a hallway.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyond-23-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhat distinguishes Maurpankhi further is its curated material palette. Walls finished with limewash exude a soft, tactile beauty, while the overall color scheme leans into neutral, earthy tones that soothe the senses. The use of natural and time-responsive materials is deliberate, reinforcing the idea that the house isn’t static – it transforms with the people inside.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576423\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576423\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Maurpankhi-Gurugram-Bungalow-House-and-Beyo